strings: <voice_0x01000EE9><se_def>Prince Charmles: So THIS is an Argon heart? But it's so small!
<voice_0x01000EEA><se_def>Prince Charmles: Looks like the Argon lizards aren't anything to worry about after all.
<voice_0x01000EEB><se_def>Prince Charmles: We'll have to keep hunting lizards until we find one big enough to do justice to my heroism!
<voice_0x01000EEC><se_high>Jessica: This from a guy who runs at the slightest hint of danger? Don't make me laugh...
<voice_0x01000EED><se_low>Yangus: Would ya look at that! He can barely 'old 'is own knife an' 'e still thinks 'e stands a chance!
<voice_0x01000EEE><se_def>Angelo: A legend in his own mind. It's as though he's forgotten who's going to be doing the actual fighting...
